snippet.title: They Are Here: Alien Abduction Horror - Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/1547540/They_Are_Here/ 

“They Are Here” - is a first-person horror story about a journalist who witnessed an alien invasion at the Grayswood farm. Explore the area armed with a flashlight. Take photos of evidence of aliens' presence and get to the bottom of the horrifying truth.
#TheyAreHereAlienAbductionHorror #TheyAreHere #horrorgaming #game #alien
